{"tid":929951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳中興向美國篤灰出賣華為","createTime":"2018-12-06T02:54:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T13:05:44.000Z","uid":5195,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1b9742acef60d18b5aed0872e1e44324cee075b6","tid":929951,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T02:54:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中興通訊（763）昨晚發公告稱，「公司管理層已決定採取相關美國法律下可採取的與美國政府命令相關的某些行動」，股票繼續停牌。該段文字難以理解，內地網上盛傳，中興通訊可能暗示將配合美方調查，轉做污點證人，向美方檢舉華為違規或交出「黑材料」，以換來一線生機。<br />\n<br />\n中興會否舉報華為暫未能確認，但篤背脊行為已早有前科。美國商務部之前已將多份中興內部機密文件放上網，其中一份《關於全面整頓和規範公司出口管制相關業務的報告》（<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2r0KkRk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2r0KkRk&d=35v5%2BV5R0wjNmYl1b1mfCf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=7a871232\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2r0KkRk</a>），獲總裁在內的四位高層簽名批示同意，當中詳細列明出口伊朗、蘇丹、朝鮮、敘利亞、古巴五大禁運國的操作情況，成為鐵證。<br />\n<br />\n在該份被標為「機密」的文件中，其中有一段提及「F7現狀」，指F7專門找到一家大型IT企業作為上述管制國項目的簽約主體，由於該企業質資較強，比中興更能隔斷風險。<br />\n<br />\n內地業界慣以「F7」作為華為的代號，因「F7」與普通話「夫妻」諧音，即英文中的Husband與Wife，與華為的英文HuaWei首個字母重合。該段文字意思為，華為亦有從事類似出口伊朗的違規業務，但所用的代理公司質資較強，所以風險較低。文件前面提及中興找的代理公司質資代理較低，但費用較便宜，所以風險較大。該段被美國查獲的中興機密文件確認，華為同樣有伊朗業務，而且情況為中興所掌握。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180426/large/1524743759_8b5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180426%2Flarge%2F1524743759_8b5c.jpg&h=1756cbef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地業界習慣以「F7」作為華為的代號，因「F7」與普通話「夫妻」諧音，即英文中的Husband與Wife，與華為的英文HuaWei首個字母重合。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180426/small/1524745350_5a88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180426%2Fsmall%2F1524745350_5a88.jpg&h=337f8e1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文件獲總裁在內的四位高層簽名批示同意，當中詳細列明出口伊朗、蘇丹、朝鮮、敘利亞、古巴五大禁運國的操作情況，成為鐵證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180426/58122087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180426%2F58122087&d=35v5%2BV5R0wjNmYl1b1mfCf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=7dc04b07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180426%2F58122087&h=bc29bff4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180426/58122087</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鬼打鬼</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ef503626ee7ee0c4b623b4ea67a8604d3f2bc49f","tid":929951,"uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T02:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁華喂出賣邊個好呢"},{"pid":"e6b4947a41d7fd8e823a3ab44b1b9d0bf5003d8e","tid":929951,"uid":60366,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T02:59:23.000Z","msg":"好似打緊Superbowl 個中場休息咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貿易戰中場要搵d野做下暖下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8097f4f41e1478669c5ec5c30ed2c954605c4c","tid":929951,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T03:02:06.000Z","msg":"垃圾，全都是垃圾郵件<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9e0c76295261b712bed55eb6973341439e5744","tid":929951,"uid":48623,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ef503626ee7ee0c4b623b4ea67a8604d3f2bc49f","tid":929951,"uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T02:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁華喂出賣邊個好呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T03:02:38.000Z","msg":"聯想 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa40