<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狗咬狗"},{"pid":"d8e3ac4137e50e974f31de0c4702d0be453c5662","tid":929951,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T03:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0baac712937b441cb6f099f038be467aeec60a31","tid":929951,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138f4fe95fc765bc5b49ffadc2a09684cc2fc11d","tid":929951,"uid":202139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6b4947a41d7fd8e823a3ab44b1b9d0bf5003d8e","tid":929951,"uid":60366,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T02:59:23.000Z","msg":"好似打緊Superbowl 個中場休息咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貿易戰中場要搵d野做下暖下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T05:06:36.000Z","msg":"唔關貿易戰事，<br />\n奧巴馬時代已開始查。"},{"pid":"db02ddd1fb9e47305c935b59d5775f26d31eedc7","tid":929951,"uid":13343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T10:57:05.000Z","msg":"華為就用d「當美國人唔識」嘅代號<br />\n<br />\n但3leaf 一 search就知邊間<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再搵埋 2011 年邊個試過收購3leaf<br />\n<br />\n就知f7係邊個<br />\n<br />\n咁d代號改嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f94006bc628d58ada1fc4cbc618f33747f0a3f4","tid":929951,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T11:07:09.000Z","msg":"爆出黎起碼美帝會比條生路佢地行下 唔爆就一野炒起晒全部人"},{"pid":"1091b30e25ae4d3ebbdf683ac6ae89b03ec81cf3","tid":929951,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:45:42.000Z","msg":"千年傳統<br />\n中國有邊次同